uch shortcut for app switching:<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;We regretfully had to temporarily drop support for this gesture due to a technical constraint. We will be bringing it back in an upcoming iOS 11.x update.<br />\n<br />\nThanks (and sorry for the inconvenience)!&rdquo;</blockquote><br />\nCraig Federighi 在回覆粉絲的郵件中提到，蘋果其實是因爲遇到一些技術上的問題，所以才會暫時砍掉這個手勢的。<br />\n<br />\n　　在郵件中，粉絲表達了希望能將這個手勢保留的願望。而 Craig Federighi  回答稱，因爲一些技術問題，我們很遺憾不得不暫時砍掉這個手勢，不過我們會在即將發佈的 iOS 11.x 更新中，重新將這個手勢帶回來。</blockquote><br />\n唔完美都推出嚟"},{"pid":"1fb1adb1d016ddba44c624fd2a36e28fc06472ea","tid":408263,"uid":83569,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T01:29:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最憎粒智障野 除非預自己用3年</blockquote><br />\n三年都禁唔壞粒home 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正確d講應該係真係開始失靈先用粒野頂住先<br />\n<br />\n平時見到d女仔用呢粒野心入面都扣d分"}]}